00:31:30,611 --> 00:31:34,052
it would actually create a really high demand for a character that we don't have a whole lot of.

572
00:31:34,072 --> 00:31:36,713
So you kind of want to gel, talk with your level designers.

573
00:31:38,020 --> 00:31:41,383
Now swappers of course were special, they had some extra rules.

574
00:31:44,145 --> 00:31:47,068
