575
00:31:47,748 --> 00:31:50,130
So the first one is synergy with the matching half.

576
00:31:50,390 --> 00:31:54,814
Now you may not always play the stink part of stink bomb.

577
00:31:55,590 --> 00:32:00,294
when you buy a stink bomb, but you bought one of them and they come together in the same box.

578
00:32:00,394 --> 00:32:02,155
So we at least know that you're putting them together.

579
00:32:02,776 --> 00:32:06,859
We also know that there was two type of kids. Kids that loved to mix up everything

580
00:32:07,300 --> 00:32:11,483
and then the slightly more OCD crowd that was like, no, everything must match perfectly.

581
00:32:11,903 --> 00:32:16,427
So we had pretty good chance that there was a large group of people playing the swappers as a normal character.

582
00:32:16,908 --> 00:32:18,109
So we tried to keep synergy.

583
00:32:19,109 --> 00:32:23,413
We also limited each parts archetype to two, almost always.

584
00:32:24,294 --> 00:32:26,855
This means that because there was five archetypes total in the game

