00:33:03,581 --> 00:33:07,001
The last one, and the most important one, and the biggest revelation for us,

596
00:33:08,082 --> 00:33:09,182
because we had some fear,

597
00:33:09,722 --> 00:33:13,983
was if anyone played Marvel Ultimate Alliance, we had a concept called Fusion,

598
00:33:14,003 --> 00:33:15,203
where if you had...

599
00:33:15,936 --> 00:33:18,578
Spider-Man and Wolverine and you put them together you get a

600
00:33:18,618 --> 00:33:22,940
brand new Spider-Man Wolverine combo move. We did not want to

601
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:25,662
do that at all because it creates a ridiculous amount of

602
00:33:25,742 --> 00:33:29,164
work. It's exponential work in fact. And exponential is a

603
00:33:29,224 --> 00:33:32,887
terrifying word. And so what we had instead was move synergy.

604
00:33:32,947 --> 00:33:36,569
Meaning if I had a character that had a fire top and an ice

