00:43:12,523 --> 00:43:15,644
And there was a particular control scheme that she used to follow.

805
00:43:15,704 --> 00:43:17,865
So once again she was kind of like a modal character.

806
00:43:18,385 --> 00:43:21,046
You would tap a button to put her into this dash move.

807
00:43:21,546 --> 00:43:23,927
Well the only way to get out of the dash move was to tap the button again.

808
00:43:24,807 --> 00:43:27,168
The reason why we made you enter the mode in the first place was because

809
00:43:27,608 --> 00:43:31,070
a younger kid has smaller hands and trying to hold multiple buttons at the same time.

810
00:43:31,924 --> 00:43:33,985
it's kind of tricky, especially for a character's core move.

811
00:43:34,645 --> 00:43:36,926
And so what would happen is they would push this mode, and they'd be like,

812
00:43:36,946 --> 00:43:39,788
ah, I'm dashing forward, I want to get out of it, and they would let go of the stick.

813
00:43:40,148 --> 00:43:41,749
